data.description: Completely remodeled 1 bedroom unit in charming Dover Park complex. Unit features sturdy vinyl plank flooring throughout. Kitchen with new cabinets, countertops and appliances. Bathroom was gutted and has a new bathtub, tile and fixtures as well. Freshly painted throughout in warm neutral tones. Complex features coin operated laundry, storage unit, clubhouse and heated pool for summertime fun. New sliders lead out to your deck overlooking a lovely wooded courtyard. For investors, unit can be rented out. Quick closing possible, so don't delay!!
